import React from 'react'
import { Container, Row, Col } from 'react-bootstrap'


function Footer() {
    return (
        
            <footer>
            <Container>
                <Row>
                <Col className="text-center py-3 "> copyright © proshop </Col>
                </Row>
            </Container>
            </footer>
        
    )
}

export default Footer
